I just got a take out from them, it’s soooo yummy 😋  Update: I’ve been ordering a lot from them, but I disappointed with my last visit. I ordered pick up two different dishes, they made it the same. and I found out about that when I already got home. So I called them to see if they could offer anything alternative, but the guy on the phone was very rude, not apologetic at all, he just told me to go back there to change it. He said I have to bring the wrong order back to them, why?????? If it’s their fault they supposed to leave this wrong order and give me the one I wanted, but he told me I have to bring that food back to them in order to get what I really ordered. Btw it’s definitely their mistake, bec when I placed the order on the phone the girl was constantly distracted to others in their language. And I made her repeat my order, even though she placed wrong order. I told that guy on the phone that he could listen to that call record as I was 💯 sure about my order he didn’t even paid attention, just told me to go back there. I didn’t wanna travel there twice if there is no apologies, no complimentary stuff for my travel back and forth, mainly they don’t appreciate my time. I didn’t order since then, and before I used to order at least twice a week. I feel so bad about that. Bottom line: bad customer service, they don’t take orders properly, by that they waste my time and money on food I didn’t order.

This is a dine in experience. Restaurant is very clean. Ordering easy and cashier guide you with patience. I ordered general tso’s chicken, shrimp, mixed vegetables, chicken wings and buffalo wings. Some with fries, some with fried rice. They have white rice option too and no extra charge for fried rice. All of them are delicious. I really liked their to-go containers which you use for dine in too. High quality microwaveable and reusable plastic. Also very reasonable price, I wouldn’t mind even little bit high but thanks for keeping low. Overall this is a 5+ take out place. Being halal is another plus. Definitely come back for pick up. Worth to drive from Staten Island. Keep doing whatever you are doing.  Note: I have been there many times since the first visit. Same quality, same price, same smile.
